ravitational skeleton approach, analytical expressions for the\nperiastron advance, the meridional Lense-Thirring precession and spin\nprecession frequency in the case of a spinning particle on a nearly circular\nequatorial orbit in Kerr spacetime, including also terms quadratic in the spin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Sep 2013 21:03:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Oct 2013 21:27:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 16 Nov 2013 21:14:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
