esides providing an account of these\npeculiarities, the model suggests that the afterglow phase may in fact begin\nbefore the RBW reaches $R \\simeq R_D$, thus introducing novel insights into the\nGRB phenomenology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Sep 2013 01:03:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
