e world around them, will enable them to\ndetermine effective intervention strategies to simultaneously optimise and\nsafeguard their interests and the interests of the environment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Sep 2013 08:34:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-04"}
