, an RCSP-based decoding error trajectory is introduced\nthat provides target error rates for the design of rate-compatible code\nfamilies for use in feedback communication systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Sep 2013 14:45:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-04"}
